          <div class="finding-body">Bike-taxi demand drops ~50% during lunch peak food-delivery window. Captains fill idle time with Ownly orders. Rapido already has 4M+ registered Captains vs Swiggy's 530K and Zomato's 440K — the supply advantage is 8–9× at the network level.</div>
