          <div class="finding-title">Restaurant anger is at historical peak</div>
          <div class="finding-body">Zomato's platform fee grew from ₹2 in 2023 to ₹14.90 in March 2026 — a 645% hike in 3 years. Swiggy hit ₹17.58. NRAI (50K+ restaurants) co-built Ownly's launch and is vocal. Supply-side tailwind this strong doesn't come often.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="finding-card good">
          <div class="finding-title">5,000 daily orders — organic, no discounts</div>
          <div class="finding-body">This is fast traction for a new food app with no cashback, no Gold-equivalent, and only one city. Zomato and Swiggy relied on heavy subsidies in their early years. Ownly's early adoption is purely price-driven — a more durable signal.</div>
