          <div class="finding-title">Swiggy sold its 12% Rapido stake</div>
          <div class="finding-body">Swiggy sold ₹2,400Cr of Rapido equity to Prosus and WestBridge within weeks of Ownly launching. That's not a portfolio rotation — it's a conflict-of-interest exit. The best external signal that incumbents see Ownly as a real threat.</div>
        </div>
