          <div class="finding-title">Viral "Food Promise" campaign</div>
          <div class="finding-body">Courtroom-themed ad satirising hidden charges went viral with restaurant owners as the primary sharers. Zero paid media spend, enormous earned reach among exactly the supply partners Ownly needed to onboard. Brilliant earned-media design.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="finding-card good">
          <div class="finding-title">15% new-to-online restaurants</div>
          <div class="finding-body">Of the first 2,300+ restaurants onboarded in Bengaluru, 15% had never done online food delivery before. That's the Meesho thesis in action — not just taking market share, but growing the addressable market.</div>
